<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l1"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> vom Eglofſtein dem <expan>Junge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l2"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt beuor <expan>H<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hanns <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Eglofſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l3">habt von des ʒugrıffs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> den Jr <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>nehſtu<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> pfıncʒtag getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l4">hett vnd auch von . <expan cert="unknown">C .</expan> ryenolts <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / der in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> fenknuſſ <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ıſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l5">etc / das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu mugt ır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteen</expan> / was wır in </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l6">den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> getan <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> / Daʒ wır des dem <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> reıche vnd vnſſelbs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l7">ſchuldıg ſein . So hat vns <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der <expan>Bıſch<ex>of</ex></expan> von <expan>wırcʒb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l8"><expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> brıef geſandt des wır eẅch ein <expan>abſchr<ex>ift</ex></expan> <expan>hıerynn<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l9">Alſo meynen auch wır hınfür darynn ʒutun . daʒ wır wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l10"><expan>ʒuu<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> margarete </ab>
