<expan>Hanns<ex>en</ex></expan> vom Eglofstein dem
                            <expan>junge<ex>n</ex></expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst bevor. <expan>H<ex>e</ex>r</expan>
                        Hanns <expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>Eglofst<ex>ein</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von des zugriffs
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, den ir <app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>nehstv<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> pfincztag</q>11.07.1420</note>
</app> getan hett und auch von <expan cert="unknown">C.</expan> Ryenolts
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        fenknuss <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ist etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu
                        mugt ir wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>, was wir in den
                                <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan> getan <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        daz wir des dem <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan> reiche und unsselbs
                        schuldig sein. So hat uns <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der <expan>bisch<ex>of</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> brief gesandt, des wir ewch ein
                                <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>hierynn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>sloss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>. Also meynen auch wir hinfür darynn zutun,
                        daz wir wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>zu v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Margarete.</ab>
</div>
